<html dir='ltr' lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width' />
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <meta name='x-apple-disable-message-reformatting' />
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <meta name='x-apple-disable-message-reformatting' />
    <meta
      name='format-detection'
      content='telephone=no,address=no,email=no,date=no,url=no'
    />
    <meta name='color-scheme' content='light' />
    <meta name='supported-color-schemes' content='light' />
    <!--$-->
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: #111;
        padding: 20px 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 20px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        position: relative;
      }

      .email-container::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 6px;
      }

      .header {
        background: #111;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(
          circle,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%,
          transparent 70%
        );
        animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      .logo {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }

      .logo h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 2.8em;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .logo .tagline {
        color: #bdc3c7;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-weight: 300;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 50px 40px;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .content h2 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-size: 1.8em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .content p {
        color: #555555;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 1.05em;
      }

      .btn-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 35px 0;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 35px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }

      .btn:hover::before {
        left: 100%;
      }

      .btn-verify {
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
        color: white !important;
      }

      .footer {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }

      .footer p {
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 0.95em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .signature {
        color: #2c3e50 !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1em !important;
      }

      .divider {
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e9ecef, #007bff, #e9ecef);
        margin: 30px 0;
        border-radius: 1px;
      }

      .security-note {
        background: #f0f9ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
      }

      .security-note p {
        color: #0369a1;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.95em;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .email-container {
          margin: 0 15px;
          border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .logo h1 {
          font-size: 2.2em;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 35px 25px;
        }

        .content h2 {
          font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .btn {
          padding: 14px 28px;
          font-size: 1em;
        }

        .footer {
          padding: 25px 25px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style='margin:0'>
    <div id='reset-template' class='template'>
      <div class='email-container'>
        <div class='header'>
          <div class='logo'>
            <h1>WARTECH</h1>
            <div class='tagline'>Warta Technologies</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='content'>
          <h2>{{title}} üîê</h2>
          <p>Hai
            <strong>{{name}}</strong>,
            {{message}}</p>
          <p>{{description}}</p>
          <div class='btn-container'>
            <a href={{url}} class='btn btn-verify'>{{subject}}</a>
          </div>
          <div class='security-note'>
            <p><strong>Penting untuk Diketahui:</strong>
              Link reset ini akan kedaluwarsa dalam 15 menit. Jika Anda merasa
              tidak mengirim permintaan ini, segera hubungi tim kami untuk
              keamanan akun Anda.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='footer'>
          <p>Jika Anda tidak melakukan permintaan ini, Anda bisa mengabaikan
            email ini dengan aman. Tidak ada perubahan yang akan dilakukan tanpa
            tindakan Anda.</p>
          <div class='divider'></div>
          <p class='signature'>Salam Inovasi,<br /><strong>Tim Wartech</strong><br
            />Advanced Technology Solutions</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>